Blurring reduces noise and smoothens the image.

cv2.blur(img, (5,5))              # Average Blur
cv2.GaussianBlur(img, (5,5), 0)   # Gaussian Blur
cv2.medianBlur(img, 5)            # Median Blur
cv2.bilateralFilter(img, 9, 75, 75) # Bilateral Filter


Average Blur → simple smoothing

Gaussian Blur → weighted smoothing

Median Blur → good for removing salt-and-pepper noise

Bilateral Filter → smooths while preserving edges

